<section class="mag-b">



	<div class="content-wrap"> 



    <div id="mjm-desc-sec">



    <h2 class="ts-18 tc-b3" style="margin-top:0px;">Current Jobs in Kenya</h2>



    <div class="mjm-desc-detail ts-13">



    MyJobMag Kenya is the leading career and job website in Kenya, connecting millions of job seekers with verified opportunities from trusted employers. We offer career tools and resources that help candidates improve their CVs, match their profiles to the right roles, and grow professionally. We also work closely with employers and recruiters, providing solutions that make it easier to attract, screen, and hire the right talent. All jobseeker services on MyJobMag Kenya are completely free. Stay connected with us via email and social media.


</div>



</div>



    </div>



</section>







